From d0c44e76b001cdeea58ab04ef2275079bdd203a4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dara Ramesh <dramesh@nvidia.com>
Date: Fri, 20 Feb 2026 08:22:14 -0800
Subject: [PATCH 36/98] adsp: cleanup legacy code

The legacy ADSP applications, such as file access and lpthread,
as well as the actmon driver, are no longer supported on T26x/T23x.

Bug 5174542

Upstream-Status: Backport
Change-Id: I3e70f11e0c09a7178f069c2423ad068dc765eea8
Signed-off-by: Dara Ramesh <dramesh@nvidia.com>
Reviewed-on: https://git-master.nvidia.com/r/c/linux-nv-oot/+/3359415
Reviewed-by: Viswanath L <viswanathl@nvidia.com>
GVS: buildbot_gerritrpt <buildbot_gerritrpt@nvidia.com>
(cherry picked from commit 97f7875469aec7f6d762bf6ce9d2844a5abbfbe3)
Signed-off-by: Matt Madison <matt@madison.systems>
